            <p id = "dText">I have gone to school for 4 years and changed my major 4 times. I find that I’m really good at doing this type of jobs. So, i’m really hoping i can get this job because I’m really excited for it. During college I made many new friends so I believe my communication skills are great. I know that I will be a good team worker and get along with everyone.</p>
